== 私人生活 ==
2006年2月，克洛斯与男友[[:en:David_Evans_Shaw|David Evans Shaw]]成婚。她曾与Cabot Wade(1969-1973)和James Marlas（1984-1987）有过两段婚姻。她的女儿Annie Starke，是她与她的男友John Starke的爱情结晶，不过两人的关系于1991年结束。她多次为[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]候选人捐款，包括[[希拉里·罗德姆·克林顿|希拉里·罗德姆·克林顿]]、[[约翰·爱德华兹|约翰·爱德华兹]]和[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]。<ref name="Opensecrets.org">{{cite web |url=http://www.opensecrets.org/indivs/search.asp?key=a4rpw&txtName=Close,%20Glenn&txtState=(all%20states)&txtAll=Y&Order=N |title=Opensecrets.org |publisher=Opensecrets.org |date= |accessdate=2010-08-22 |archive-date=2020-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327080221/http://www.opensecrets.org/indivs/search.asp?key=a4rpw&txtName=Close,%20Glenn&txtState=(all%20states)&txtAll=Y&Order=N |dead-url=yes }}</ref>她也是一名知名的爱狗人士，曾在Fetchdog.com上开设专栏，采访其他名人讲诉他们与他们的爱犬之间的亲密情感。<ref name="fetchdog">{{Cite web |url=http://www.fetchdog.com/blogs/livelylicks |title=fetchdog.com |access-date=2011-12-17 |archive-date=2012-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501004418/http://www.fetchdog.com/blogs/livelylicks |dead-url=no }}</ref>她也宣称，她有其自己的[[DNA测序|DNA测序]]。<ref name="Biotechniques">{{cite news| title=BioTechniques – First named female genome sequenced| url=http://www.biotechniques.com/news/First-named-female-genome-sequenced/biotechniques-204525.html?utm_source=BioTechniques+Newsletters+%26+e-Alerts&utm_campaign=d473e565ff-BTN+Weekly&utm_medium=email| access-date=2011-12-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110928212048/http://www.biotechniques.com/news/First-named-female-genome-sequenced/biotechniques-204525.html?utm_source=BioTechniques+Newsletters+&+e-Alerts&utm_campaign=d473e565ff-BTN+Weekly&utm_medium=email| archive-date=2011-09-28| dead-url=yes}}</ref>

